'''Crewe''' is a [[Impact crater|crater]] approximately 3&nbsp;km in diameter lying situated within the [[Margaritifer Sinus quadrangle]] (MC-19) region of the planet [[Mars]], located at 25° South, 10° West.

The crater was named after the town of [[Crewe]], [[Cheshire]], [[England]].

